---
title: HelloHero: One-Pot Chermoula Venison Pilaf with Yoghurt & Crushed Peanuts
description: One-pot cooking isn’t just convenient, it’s also full of lots of lovely flavours as everything comes together. Take a beef and venison veggie pilaf, the Moroccan and chermoula spices melt in the bowl. One irresistible and easy dinner coming right up!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
